title: We Can't Believe This Festival Has Been Canceled + Moe Wasn't Prepared To Attend *This* Restaurant
description:
Moe has a bone to pick with Keity over a restaurant they went to with Romeo this past weekend. He let her pick the place they attended. But when they arrive, there were a lot of surprises they weren't prepared for. But first, need to talk about Music Midtown.
